Chorshanba: Broadcasting va Real-Time Integration
Maqsad: Real-time ilova funksiyalarini yaratish.

O‘rganish:
Broadcastingning asosiy tushunchalari.
Public va Private kanallar.
Laravel Websockets yoki Pusher bilan ishlash.
Amaliyot:

Oddiy chat ilovasi uchun xabar yuborishni broadcasting orqali amalga oshiring.
Foydalanuvchining statusini real-time’da yangilaydigan broadcast yozing.